<div id='instructions' class="z-depth-1">
  <span class='close'><i class="material-icons c-orange">close</i></span>
<% if current_user.category == 'client' %>
    <p>We are reviewing your project's feasability.</p>
    <p>Please answer topics to ensure feasibility of your project.</p>
    <p>Do not hesitate to open topics if needed or upload files if necessary.</p>
<% elsif current_user.category == 'methods' %>
  <p>You know need to assess the project feasability.</p>
  <p>Open topics to communicate or ask infos to the client or within your team.</p>
  <p>You can upload new version of files and track changes.</p>
  <p>Please ensure all topics are reviewed before going to next step</p>
<% else %>
  <p>This an overview of the project today.</p>
  <p>Reading the topics will keep you up-to-date .</p>
<% end %>
</div>
<br>

<div id='design-analisys-state'>
  <% if current_user.category == 'methods' %>
    <div class="col s12">
      <%= render 'projects/form', specs: @project.specs %>
    </div>
  <% else %>
    <div class="col s12">
      <h4>Project Title: <%= @project.title %></h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Client name: <%= @project.client %></li>
        <li>Main Contact: <%= @project.project_users.first.user.name %></li>
        <li>Thal√®s ref: <%= @project.thales_id %></li>
        <li>Client ref: <%= @project.client_project_id %></li>
      </ul>
      <p>Part Functionnality: <%= @project.part_functionality %></p>
      <p><em>Notes: <%= simple_format @project.notes %></em></p>
      <table class='responsive-table'>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Specs</th>
            <th>Option</th>
            <th>Description</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% @project.specs.each do | spec | %>
            <tr>
              <td><%= spec.type %></td>
              <td><%= spec.title %></td>
              <td><%= spec.description %></td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
